<emphasis bold="true" box="[383,404,1920,1946]" pageId="32" pageNumber="141">D</emphasis>
. Tip of inner palea. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[662,682,1920,1946]" pageId="32" pageNumber="141">E</emphasis>
